 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                    Retail      Office    Industrial   All Properties
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Year to Dec 91      -0.7         -9.1       -0.5           -4.0
Quarter to Dec 91   -0.1         -3.2       -0.9           -1.5
