FT  06 FEB 92 / Appointments: Financial moves
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Co-op Bank has appointed two new executive directors, Gordon Younger (46)
and Michael Firth (45). They and Ken Lewis, head of personnel, will serve on
a newly-established executive committee along with the three existing
executive directors of the bank.
