sales of DM10.25bn.
Co op was on the brink of bankruptcy when ASKO bought it at the end of 1990
and has since gone through a hard hitting restructuring.
Germany's Treuhand privatisation agency hopes to sell the east German
chemical manufacturer Buna and the chemical divisions of Leuna to western
investors by the summer.
